name: The Sorceress Room
description:
First piece of #WitchingHourOnHEN

The Sorceress Room belonged to her mother, and her grandmother before. It's full of books with ancient spells, potions and priceless knwoledge.
Most of her power comes from knowing how to mix herbs and other resources from Mother Earth.
If you do anything to damage the forest harmony... you better hide before she finds you. She'll have no mercy.

She's always in company of her dog, the most special guardian and friend.
